title: [1508521049] Ploughman's Lunch with Beer Soaked Bread | Gordon Ramsay
description:
A ploughman’s lunch is a pub classic - Gordon offers his modern twist with beer-soaked bread and light, fragrant pickled onions. Beautiful.
